d be:\\n```yaml\\nif: inputs.agent == 'roger-roger'\\n```\\n\\nAs-is, the verify step **never runs** in the isolated workflow, making it dead code. The `e2e.yml` workflow correctly uses `matrix.agent` since it does have a matrix.\\n\\n**Bug: `rc` may be unset in `mise-tasks/test/e2e/roger-roger`**\\n\\nLine 39 uses `|| rc=$?` but `rc` is never initialized, and line 45 does `exit \\\"${rc:-0}\\\"`. This works via the `:-0` fallback, but it's inconsistent with the canary script which initializes `rc=0` up front. Minor, pre-existing.\\n\\n### Suggestions\\n\\n**1. Canary script: first `|| rc=$?` overwrites, second is lost**\\n\\nIn `mise-tasks/test/e2e/canary`, `rc=0` is initialized, then both gotestsum invocations use `|| rc=$?`. If vogon fails (rc=1) but roger-roger succeeds (rc=0), the final `rc` is 0 — masking the vogon failure. Consider:\\n\\n```sh\\nrc=0\\n... || rc=$?\\n... || rc=$?   # this overwrites the previous failure\\n```\\n\\nA simple fix:\\n```sh\\nrc=0\\n... || { rc=$?; }\\n... || { rc=$?; }\\n# becomes:\\nvogon_rc=0; rr_rc=0\\n... || vogon_rc=$?\\n... || rr_rc=$?\\nexit $(( vogon_rc > rr_rc ? vogon_rc : rr_rc ))\\n```\\n\\nOr more simply: `|| rc=1` instead of `|| rc=$?` to accumulate failures.\\n\\n**2. Duplicated preflight checks**\\n\\nThe `command -v roger-roger` / `command -v entire-agent-roger-roger` check is copy-pasted across `canary` and `roger-roger` scripts. Not critical for 2 scripts, but worth noting.\\n\\n**3. The \\\"Potential fix for pull request finding\\\" commits**\\n\\nThe last two commits (`26192dd4`, `0c60996e`) both say \\\"Potential fix for pull request finding\\\" — these seem like debug/iteration commits unrelated to the PR's purpose. Consider squashing before merge.\\n\\n### Positives\\n\\n- Clean separation: mise manages the tooling, scripts just assert presence\\n- Good preflight checks — no silent pass if binaries are missing\\n- Per-agent artifact files (`test-events-vogon.json`, `test-events-roger-roger.json`) avoid clobbering\\n- CI is passing\\n\\n### Verdict\\n\\nThe `matrix.agent` vs `inputs.agent` bug in `e2e-isolated.yml` should be fixed — it's a no-op today. The `rc` overwrite in the canary script should also be addressed since it can mask failures. Otherwise, solid change.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":228,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":34629,\"output_tokens\":1016,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":228,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CZ6vcoqHMg5CzDKKqBEaJ\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"d17154c8-d564-4839-bc6f-724b4868ff45\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-16T14:35:11.460Z\",\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/nodo/work/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"77726bd4-421e-44dd-9836-b50e4768bfa2\",\"version\":\"2.1.76\",\"gitBranch\":\"nodo/external-agents-e2e-canary\",\"slug\":\"dynamic-orbiting-pelican\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"d17154c8-d564-4839-bc6f-724b4868ff45\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks claude-code stop\"},\"parentToolUseID\":\"efd17fdf-f586-4f7f-b5df-5357dd271d2e\",\"toolUseID\":\"efd17fdf-f586-4f7f-b5df-5357dd271d2e\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-16T14:35:11.497Z\",\"uuid\":\"6849220c-a874-43b7-aa79-5d0a522488d6\",\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/nodo/work/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"77726bd4-421e-44dd-9836-b50e4768bfa2\",\"version\":\"2.1.76\",\"gitBranch\":\"nodo/external-agents-e2e-canary\",\"slug\":\"dynamic-orbiting-pelican\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"6849220c-a874-43b7-aa79-5d0a522488d6\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"stop_hook_summary\",\"hookCount\":1,\"hookInfos\":[{\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT